~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        Home Assistant Core - Xigmanas Bastille Extension
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Basic Home Assistant Core service control:
    service homeassistant [ restart | start | status | stop ]

- Upgrade Home Assistant Core:
    service homeassistant upgrade

- Check the Home Assistant Core configuration:
    service homeassistant check_config
    
- Home Assistant Core default log file locations:
    /home/homeassistant/homeassistant/home-assistant.log
    /var/log/homeassistant_daemon.log

